<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="obvious-adj">obvious <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɒbviəs/    美 /'ɑːbviəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-clear-apparent">1.★ <strong>明显的；显而易见的(clear / apparent)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make an obvious mistake
犯明显的错误</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is obvious to</strong> the students <strong>that</strong> they should get well prepared for their future.
学生们很清楚他们应该为将来做好充分的准备。</p><footer>2009 天津</footer></div></div>